hen not watching TV programming. <br /><br /> Boasting a slimming tapered bezel and attractive front panel gradation, the new Horizon design creates a more modern, elegant appearance that also adds a subtle luminance to the logo to further its stylish appeal. Other features include MP3 playback via the integrated USB port, a PC input, and a removable stand.</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '<p class=\"product-promo-text\"><span class=\"product-promo-header\">FREE US shipping over $100!</span><span class=\"product-promo-body\">Orders within next 2 days will be shipped on Monday</span></p>');
